Stangerson,
Kemball,
Johnston,
and
Drebber,
who
were
the
four
principal
Elders.
On
the
farm
thus
acquired
John
Ferrier
built
himself
a
substantial
log
house,
which
received
so
many
additions
in
succeeding
years
that
