or
met
her
mounted
upon
her
father's
mustang,
and
managing
it
with
all
the
ease
and
grace
of
a
true
child
of
the
West.
So
the
bud
blossomed
into
a
flower,
and
the
year
which
saw
her
father
the
richest
of
the
farmers
left
